claim: The Theory of Everything was adapted from a memior by Anthony McCarten from 1998.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Theory of Everything is a 2014 British biographical romantic drama film directed by James Marsh and adapted by Anthony McCarten from the memoir Travelling to Infinity : My Life with Stephen by Jane Wilde Hawking , which deals with her relationship with her ex-husband , theoretical physicist Stephen Hawking , his diagnosis of amyotrophic lateral sclerosis  (  ALS , also known as Lou Gehrig 's disease or motor neurone disease  )  , and his success in physics .
